<div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><h1>CAM3D</h1><p><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/3581DB93-A6AD-C05D-9F99-D2AB75A13237.png" style="width: 234px;" class="fr-fic fr-dii fr-fil">CAM3D creates data for machining curved surfaces of 3D CAD models that consist of surfaces as well as solids.</p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><br></p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/cam3d-P0032"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Read More &rarr;</span></a></p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><br></p><h1>Basic Function of CAM (DB)</h1><p><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/BFBF239A-20CD-39E1-9923-6B751CB7B375.png" style="width: 234px;" class="fr-fic fr-dii fr-fil">CADmeister/CAM provides operational modes for skillful expert users and beginners.</p><p><br></p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/basic-function-of-cam-db-P0033"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Read More &rarr;</span></a></p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><br></p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><br></p><h1>Basic Function of CAM (NC)</h1><p><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/928043AC-01CB-9568-B5E6-13DBA7EF43A7.png" style="width: 234px;" class="fr-fic fr-dii fr-fil">Capabilities of creating NC Data that support &rsquo;3-axis machining devices&rsquo;, &rsquo;Table 5-axis machining devices&rsquo;, and &rsquo;Attachment 5-axis machining devices&rsquo; are provided.</p><p><br></p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/basic-function-of-cam-nc-P0034"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Read More &rarr;</span></a></p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><br></p><h1>CAM2D</h1><p><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/85E9F517-0E52-6875-C440-FAFCFF16E82D.png" class="fr-fic fr-dii fr-fil" style="width: 234px;">CAM2D is capable of seamlessly integrating the features of CAD and CAM systems. It enables users out in the manufacturing field to create 2D machining paths which</p><p><br></p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/cam2d-P0035"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Read More &rarr;</span></a></p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><br></p><h1>CAMEDIT</h1><p><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/9E609B2B-1E83-AC6E-63B7-B556146126D4.png" class="fr-fic fr-dii fr-fil" style="width: 234px;">CAMEDIT has various types of editing capabilities. It enables users to edit paths highly efficiently through easy operations. are used for the commands of &rsquo;Profile Machining&rsquo; , &rsquo;Pocket Machining&rsquo; , and &rsquo;Hole Machining&rsquo; through simple operations.</p><p><br></p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/camedit-P0036"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Read More &rarr;</span></a><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/basic-function-of-cam-nc-P0034"></a></p><p><br></p><h1>CAM-DX</h1><p><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/C3E753C0-6EC9-664A-EEFB-E55103F38397.png" class="fr-fic fr-dii fr-fil" style="width: 234px;">CAM-DX supports high-speed and high-quality machining methods as well as the conventional machining methods. Thus, CAM-DX can respond to a wide variety of users&rsquo; needs.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/cam-dx-P0037"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Read More &rarr;</span></a></p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><br></p><h1>CAM-ADV</h1><p><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/4E797CB8-C024-6F24-6935-91B5103A0240.png" class="fr-fic fr-dii fr-fil" style="width: 234px;">CAM-ADV enables work flows without wastes and reworks, provided that it is operated as an add-on function for CADmeiser/CAM.</p><p><br></p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/cam-adv-P0038"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Read More &rarr;</span></a></p><p><br></p><h1>CAM-STL</h1><p><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/6925C34B-C701-05FE-277C-9AEF97FF3C2D.png" class="fr-fic fr-dii fr-fil" style="width: 234px;">CAM-STL creates paths on the basis of STL figures such as measurement results and models that consist of combinations of surfaces and solids.</p><p><br></p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/cam-stl-P0039"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Read More &rarr;</span></a><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/basic-function-of-cam-nc-P0034"></a></p><p><br></p><h1>3DPROFILE</h1><p><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/58280E48-83D4-6A27-992A-A2E4412A0875.png" class="fr-fic fr-dii fr-fil" style="width: 234px;">3DPROFILE has various 3D capabilities of machining and interference prevention. It supports automatic profile machining from preliminary rough processing through to finishing.</p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/3dprofile-P0040"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Read More &rarr;</span></a><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/basic-function-of-cam-nc-P0034"></a></p><p><br></p><h1>CAM-STRUCTURE</h1><p><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/C0F2F69E-D276-54F6-DAA5-58B3EF1848DE.png" class="fr-fic fr-dii fr-fil" style="width: 234px;">CAM-STRUCTURE is capable of creating data for machining a ferrous die for accepting a press die through simple operations on solid data. (Note that the ferrous die is referred to as a &rsquo;Structure&rsquo; and the press die is referred to as an &rsquo;Insert&rsquo;.) CAM-STRUCTURE improves the precision of machining a Structure and reduces workloads.</p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/cam-structure-P0041"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Read More &rarr;</span></a><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/basic-function-of-cam-nc-P0034"></a></p><p><br></p><h1>FM-CAM2</h1><p><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/43A9DB6E-1A6D-398B-2351-C9ED2916A333.png" class="fr-fic fr-dii fr-fil" style="width: 234px;">FM-CAM2 is a support tool for processing full-mold models through an effective use of 3D solid models.</p><p><br></p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/fm-cam2-P0042"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Read More &rarr;</span></a><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/basic-function-of-cam-nc-P0034"></a></p><p><br></p><h1>CAM-ATTRIBUTE</h1><p><img src="/uelthai/_content_html_editor_upload/images/9FE9ADFF-8C3C-7247-39F8-5564CFF60752.png" class="fr-fic fr-dii fr-fil" style="width: 234px;">CAM-ATTRIBUTE automatically creates and standardizes data for hole machining based on the 2D/3D attribute data and geometric data that have been assigned for hole machining.</p><p><br></p><p style="margin-left: 20px;"><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/cam-attribute-P0043"><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Read More &rarr;</span></a><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/basic-function-of-cam-nc-P0034"></a><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/basic-function-of-cam-nc-P0034"></a></p><p><br></p><p><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/basic-function-of-cam-nc-P0034"></a></p><p><a href="https://singhadevelop-test.com/uelthai/basic-function-of-cam-nc-P0034"></a></p></div><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p></div><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font